00:53:52,854 --> 00:53:53,688
‚ÄéThank you.

691
00:53:53,772 --> 00:53:55,941
‚ÄéSorry, I lost your gym clothes.

692
00:53:56,024 --> 00:53:58,026
‚ÄéIt's my birthday tomorrow.
‚ÄéCan you buy me foundation?

693
00:53:59,069 --> 00:53:59,903
‚ÄéIt looked like‚Ä¶

694
00:54:01,237 --> 00:54:03,365
‚Äéshe was just using her.

695
00:54:06,868 --> 00:54:09,120
‚ÄéI had no idea.

696
00:54:09,204 --> 00:54:12,791
‚ÄéI pray

697
00:54:12,874 --> 00:54:16,044
‚ÄéFor you

698
00:54:16,127 --> 00:54:19,839
‚ÄéI pray

699
00:54:19,923 --> 00:54:23,677
‚ÄéYou'll be protected

700
00:54:23,760 --> 00:54:28,264
‚ÄéSo that my hopes reach you--

701
00:54:29,432 --> 00:54:30,266
‚ÄéKim Min-ji.

702
00:54:30,350 --> 00:54:33,144
‚ÄéAt least help me clean
‚Äéif you're staying home on the weekend.

703
00:54:33,228 --> 00:54:34,813
‚ÄéWhy are you holed up in your room?

704
00:54:35,313 --> 00:54:36,731
‚ÄéGo hang out with your friends instead.

705
00:54:36,815 --> 00:54:38,566
‚ÄéIt's hot outside.

706
00:54:38,650 --> 00:54:39,901
‚ÄéIt's hot in your room too.

707
00:54:41,945 --> 00:54:43,196
‚ÄéTake this and come out.

708
00:55:01,715 --> 00:55:03,299
‚ÄéI didn't do anything wrong.

709
00:55:04,009 --> 00:55:06,011
‚ÄéShe and her girls kept harassing me.

710
00:55:06,553 --> 00:55:08,638
‚ÄéI took it for as long as I could
‚Äébefore fighting back!

711
00:55:08,722 --> 00:55:09,681
‚ÄéKim Min-ji.

712
00:55:10,515 --> 00:55:11,349
‚ÄéBe quiet.

713
00:55:13,810 --> 00:55:15,353
‚ÄéJeez, wash your clothes.

714
00:55:17,647 --> 00:55:19,107
‚ÄéI said don't look at me like that!

715
00:55:19,607 --> 00:55:20,900
‚ÄéThat's enough.

716
00:55:22,318 --> 00:55:25,113
‚ÄéStop picking on that pathetic kid.

717
00:55:29,284 --> 00:55:30,118
‚ÄéCome out.

718
00:55:41,588 --> 00:55:42,589
‚ÄéWhy?

719
00:55:44,424 --> 00:55:46,301
‚ÄéWhy didn't I notice sooner?

720
00:55:50,472 --> 00:55:51,306
‚ÄéHey.

721
00:55:51,848 --> 00:55:52,974
‚ÄéGet it together.

722
00:55:53,725 --> 00:55:55,435
‚ÄéThere's no time to get emotional.

723
00:55:58,146 --> 00:56:00,315
‚ÄéIt must've been so hard for her.

724
00:56:01,316 --> 00:56:02,233
‚ÄéMy poor Min-ji‚Ä¶

725
00:56:03,610 --> 00:56:04,903
‚ÄéI know you've tried hard.

726
00:56:05,862 --> 00:56:07,489
‚ÄéAnd I know you're hurting a lot.

727
00:56:09,199 --> 00:56:10,283
‚ÄéHan-soo.

728
00:56:10,366 --> 00:56:11,618
‚ÄéBut you're her dad.

729
00:56:13,453 --> 00:56:15,288
‚ÄéSo let's find Min-ji first.

730
00:56:15,789 --> 00:56:17,707
‚ÄéYou can't apologize unless you do.

731
00:56:32,472 --> 00:56:33,348
‚ÄéSo?

732
00:56:34,015 --> 00:56:35,266
‚ÄéWhere did you get this again?

733
00:56:35,350 --> 00:56:36,226
‚ÄéSorry?

734
00:56:36,893 --> 00:56:38,478
‚ÄéAt Hwasin Station.

735
00:56:39,604 --> 00:56:41,397
‚ÄéI took it from a homeless man.

736
00:56:43,274 --> 00:56:44,275
‚ÄéLet's go.

737
00:56:51,616 --> 00:56:53,201
‚ÄéHere you are.

738
00:57:03,044 --> 00:57:04,712
‚ÄéFake 66.

739
00:57:17,892 --> 00:57:20,812
‚ÄéAGENT KIM REACTIVATED

740
00:57:20,895 --> 00:57:27,694
‚ÄéEPILOGUE

741
00:57:45,378 --> 00:57:46,379
‚ÄéName?

742
00:57:50,049 --> 00:57:50,925
‚ÄéAge?

743
00:57:54,679 --> 00:57:56,347
‚ÄéFamily?

744
00:57:58,475 --> 00:58:00,059
‚ÄéRight.

745
00:58:00,143 --> 00:58:03,438
‚ÄéWhat's the point of any of this?

746
00:58:03,521 --> 00:58:08,943
‚ÄéYour name and identity
‚Äéare all a secret anyway, right?

747
00:58:10,403 --> 00:58:12,489
‚ÄéWhy are you keeping me alive?

748
00:58:12,572 --> 00:58:14,782
‚ÄéThat's a good question.

749
00:58:15,700 --> 00:58:16,784
‚ÄéWell, let's see.

750
00:58:16,868 --> 00:58:20,705
‚ÄéKilling you won't speed up reunification.

751
00:58:21,414 --> 00:58:23,041
‚ÄéAnd depending on the situation,

752
00:58:23,124 --> 00:58:25,793
‚Äéwe might be able to help each other out.

753
00:58:26,461 --> 00:58:27,962
‚ÄéI have this feeling

754
00:58:28,630 --> 00:58:32,383
‚Äéthat you could be
‚Äéof some sort of help to us.

755
00:58:32,467 --> 00:58:33,468
‚ÄéYeah, a gut feeling.

756
00:58:34,052 --> 00:58:36,054
‚ÄéAre you asking me to betray my homeland?

757
00:58:36,888 --> 00:58:38,723
‚ÄéGoodness.

758
00:58:38,806 --> 00:58:42,727
‚ÄéHow can a man with no name, age, or family

759
00:58:42,810 --> 00:58:44,187
‚Äéhave a homeland?

760
00:58:52,278 --> 00:58:54,906
‚ÄéHere comes the guy
‚Äéwho hunts down people like you.

761
00:58:55,657 --> 00:58:56,491
‚ÄéCome in.

762
00:59:02,121 --> 00:59:04,040
‚ÄéGoodness.

763
00:59:04,123 --> 00:59:06,626
‚ÄéLook who's here to grace this fine place
‚Äéwith their lowly presence.

764
00:59:06,709 --> 00:59:08,503
‚ÄéIt's Park Jin-cheol.

765
00:59:09,087 --> 00:59:09,963
‚ÄéLife or death.

766
00:59:10,672 --> 00:59:11,548
‚ÄéFight to the end!

767
00:59:16,594 --> 00:59:17,929
‚ÄéFrom up north

768
00:59:19,138 --> 00:59:20,223
‚Äéand down south.

769
00:59:21,307 --> 00:59:22,433
‚ÄéGo on.

770
00:59:23,184 --> 00:59:24,477
‚ÄéGreet your fellow top dog.

771
00:59:25,270 --> 00:59:26,145
‚ÄéIs this that buddy?

772
00:59:26,229 --> 00:59:28,856
‚ÄéHe's not quite a buddy yet.

773
00:59:30,400 --> 00:59:31,734
‚ÄéHey, comrade.

774
00:59:33,278 --> 00:59:36,531
‚ÄéBefore we decide
‚Äéwhether you'll be our buddy or a commie,

775
00:59:37,407 --> 00:59:39,576
‚Äélet's assess your skills first.

776
00:59:41,202 --> 00:59:42,579
‚ÄéDon't kill him just yet.

777
00:59:43,454 --> 00:59:45,707
‚ÄéA soldier either kills or gets killed.

778
01:00:04,267 --> 01:00:05,101
‚ÄéDon't hold back

779
01:00:06,519 --> 01:00:07,395
‚Äéif you want to live.

780
01:00:09,647 --> 01:00:11,065
‚ÄéIf I want to live?

781
01:00:13,651 --> 01:00:17,030
‚ÄéI have no desire to live.

782
01:00:18,698 --> 01:00:19,699
‚ÄéI'm just‚Ä¶

783
01:00:21,451 --> 01:00:24,203
‚Äékeeping the promise I made
‚Äéto my only friend.

784
01:00:27,332 --> 01:00:28,291
‚ÄéI like that.

785
01:00:32,378 --> 01:00:33,630
‚ÄéWhat's your name?

786
01:00:35,465 --> 01:00:36,424
‚ÄéIt's 73.

787
01:00:37,342 --> 01:00:38,176
‚ÄéNo.

788
01:00:42,639 --> 01:00:43,681
‚ÄéIt's 66.

789
01:00:46,392 --> 01:00:47,685
‚ÄéBring it on, 66.

790
01:01:37,193 --> 01:01:40,822
‚ÄéAGENT KIM REACTIVATED

791
01:01:43,032 --> 01:01:46,035
‚ÄéI expected someone would be watching me.

792
01:01:47,453 --> 01:01:50,540
‚ÄéIf he doesn't want his precious daughter
‚Äéto go to prison‚Ä¶

793
01:01:50,623 --> 01:01:51,457
‚ÄéCrush him.

794
01:01:54,335 --> 01:01:55,670
‚ÄéStop!

795
01:01:55,753 --> 01:01:57,046
‚ÄéWhat are you, a damn deer?!

796
01:01:58,172 --> 01:01:59,924
‚ÄéYou know whose phone this is, don't you?

797
01:02:00,007 --> 01:02:01,718
‚ÄéDid you check if she was dead?

798
01:02:01,801 --> 01:02:02,969
‚ÄéPromise me‚Ä¶

799
01:02:04,721 --> 01:02:06,347
‚Äéyou'll survive.

800
01:02:06,431 --> 01:02:09,809
‚ÄéI'll take good care of the body
‚Äéin the meantime.

801
01:02:12,854 --> 01:02:17,859
‚ÄéSubtitle translation by: Jenny Kim
